extendedInfo.description: StoneWater Church exists to REACH people with the life changing message of Jesus Christ and to EQUIP them to become committed followers of Him so that they can go and do the same.Welcome to the official StoneWater Church app for your mobile device.This app gives you access to sermons, campus locations and service times, church events, and other information.For more information about StoneWater Church, please visit us at www.StoneWaterChurch.com

reviews.title: Love!
reviews.comment: Love love love Stonewater and was very sad to leave this church to move to SC. Thanks for making an app. I still listen to you guys all the time.Plz pray we find a church over here that we love just as much as Stonewater.keep doing what yall are doing.I\'m a preachers kid and never felt confortable at a church until I found you guys! <3
